# OpenID Connect / UserInfo errors
E21000 = The access token is invalid.
E21001 = The access token does not have the required scope.
E21002 = User not found.
E21003 = The post_logout_redirect_uri is not registered for this client.
E21004 = The id_token_hint issuer is invalid.
E21005 = The post_logout_redirect_uri is invalid.
E21006 = The client_id parameter is required for this logout request.
E21007 = The client_id parameter is invalid for this logout request.
E21008 = Failed to look up the logout client.
E21009 = Logout client not found.
E21010 = The id_token_hint parameter is invalid.
E21011 = The id_token_hint parameter is required for this logout request.
